---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Hire a 3D Chalk Artist and Mural Artist"
description: "Hire 3D chalk artist and 3D mural artist Chris Carlson. Tell me about your event, brand activation, or wall and I'll get back to you with a quote. Based in Denver, available worldwide."
permalink: /contact/
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.8rem)">
      <p class="eyebrow">Start a project</p>
      <h1 class="display">Let's talk<br>about your idea</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <form class="reveal" data-contact-form action="{{ site.formspreeEndpoint }}" method="POST">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="project">Tell me about your project</label>
          <textarea id="project" name="message" placeholder="Tell me about the space, the date, and what you have in mind. Walls, floors, events, and festivals all welcome." required></textarea>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New project inquiry from chriscarlsonart.com">
        <!-- Honeypot: hidden from people, catches spam bots. -->
        <input type="text" name="_gotcha" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;opacity:0;height:0;width:0">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send project details <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></button>
        <p class="form-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
        <p class="form-note">I read every message and reply with a quote, usually within a couple of days.</p>
      </form>

      <aside class="contact-aside reveal">
        <h3 class="h3">Prefer email?</h3>
        <p>Reach me directly and I'll get right back to you.</p>
        <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:2rem">Helpful to include</h3>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>The surface (wall, floor, or both) and rough size</li>
          <li>Your location and the event date</li>
          <li>The theme, brand, or feeling you want</li>
          <li>Whether it's temporary chalk or a lasting mural</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="social-row">
          <a href="{{ site.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
          <a href="{{ site.social.facebook }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a>
          <a href="{{ site.social.etsy }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Etsy</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--concrete">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Common questions</p>
      <h2 class="h2">Hiring a 3D chalk artist or mural artist</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prose reveal" style="max-width:46rem">
      <h3 class="h3">How much does it cost to hire a 3D chalk artist?</h3>
      <p>Every project is quoted individually based on size, complexity, days on site, and travel. Send me the details through the form above and I'll come back with a clear quote.</p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:2rem">Do you travel for commissions?</h3>
      <p>Yes. I'm based in Denver, Colorado and available for hire anywhere in the world. Travel costs are included in your quote up front.</p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:2rem">How long does a piece take?</h3>
      <p>Most 3D chalk art pieces take one to three days on site. Murals depend on size and surface, and I'll give you a timeline with your quote.</p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:2rem">What surfaces can you work on?</h3>
      <p>Streets, sidewalks, plazas, indoor floors, and walls. I can also paint the artwork on canvas or vinyl in my studio and install the finished piece on site.</p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:2rem">Can you include our brand or product in the artwork?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Logos, products, and characters are a regular part of my commissioned work for brand activations and events.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

